## FORBIDDEN ACTIONS

### Never Do
- Create mock/fake data for production
- Skip ethical boundary checks
- Trade on mainnet without testnet validation
- Commit credentials or API keys
- Disable logging in production
- Override Corporate Will rejections

### Always Verify
- Test in testnet before mainnet
- Validate all external API responses
- Check rate limits before bulk operations
- Verify data integrity after migrations

## EMERGENCY PROTOCOLS

### On Critical Error
1. Stop all trading operations immediately
2. Emit preservation alert
3. Backup current state
4. Notify human operator
5. Enter safe mode (read-only)

### On Ethical Violation Attempt
1. Reject operation immediately
2. Log violation details
3. Emit corporate will alert
4. Block repeat attempts

